---
import PageLayout from '../layout/page.layout.astro';
---

<PageLayout>
    <!-- HERO SECTION -->
    <section
        class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-600 via-purple-600 to-pink-600 py-24 lg:py-32">
        <!-- Background Animation Elements -->
        <div class="absolute inset-0">
            <div
                class="absolute top-10 left-10 h-20 w-20 animate-pulse rounded-full bg-white opacity-10">
            </div>
            <div
                class="absolute right-10 bottom-10 h-16 w-16 animate-pulse rounded-full bg-white opacity-10 delay-1000">
            </div>
            <div
                class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/4 h-12 w-12 animate-pulse rounded-full bg-white opacity-10 delay-500">
            </div>
            <div
                class="absolute top-20 right-1/4 h-24 w-24 animate-bounce rounded-full bg-white opacity-5 delay-300">
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Geometric Patterns -->
        <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
            <div
                class="animate-spin-slow absolute top-16 left-16 h-32 w-32 rotate-45 border-2 border-white">
            </div>
            <div
                class="absolute right-16 bottom-16 h-24 w-24 rotate-12 animate-pulse border-2 border-white">
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 text-center lg:px-8">
            <div class="space-y-8">
                <div
                    class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-white/20 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm">
                    <span class="mr-2">👋</span>
                    Bizi Tanıyın
                </div>

                <h1
                    class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
                    <span class="block">Kurumsal</span>
                    <span
                        class="block bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-300 via-orange-300 to-pink-300 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
                        Vorthx Dijital
                    </span>
                </h1>

                <p
                    class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-xl leading-relaxed text-blue-100">
                    İnovasyon ve teknoloji tutkusuyla hareket eden, müşteri
                    odaklı çözümler üreten dijital ajansınız. Hayallerinizi
                    gerçeğe dönüştürüyoruz.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- STORY SECTION -->
    <section class="py-20 lg:py-28">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
                <h2
                    class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
                    Hikayemiz
                </h2>
                <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600">
                    2020 yılında kurulan Vorthx Dijital, dijital dünyada fark
                    yaratma vizyonuyla yola çıktı.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-2xl lg:max-w-none">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 lg:grid-cols-2">
                    <div class="flex flex-col">
                        <div
                            class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-indigo-600">
                            <svg
                                class="h-8 w-8 text-white"
                                fill="none"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                stroke-width="1.5"
                                stroke="currentColor">
                                <path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    d="M12 18v-5.25m0 0a6.01 6.01 0 001.5-.189m-1.5.189a6.01 6.01 0 01-1.5-.189m3.75 7.478a12.06 12.06 0 01-4.5 0m4.5 0a12.045 12.045 0 010-4.5m0 4.5h-4.5m0-4.5a12.045 12.045 0 010-4.5m4.5 0h-4.5m0 4.5V9.75"
                                ></path>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="mt-6 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
                            Misyonumuz
                        </h3>
                        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
                            İşletmelerin dijital dönüşüm süreçlerinde rehber
                            olmak, teknolojinin gücünü kullanarak onların
                            büyümesine katkı sağlamak. Her projeye özel çözümler
                            geliştirerek, müşterilerimizin hedeflerine
                            ulaşmalarını sağlıyoruz.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex flex-col">
                        <div
                            class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-purple-600">
                            <svg
                                class="h-8 w-8 text-white"
                                fill="none"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                stroke-width="1.5"
                                stroke="currentColor">
                                <path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    d="M2.036 12.322a1.012 1.012 0 010-.639C3.423 7.51 7.36 4.5 12 4.5c4.638 0 8.573 3.007 9.963 7.178.07.207.07.431 0 .639C20.577 16.49 16.64 19.5 12 19.5c-4.638 0-8.573-3.007-9.963-7.178z"
                                ></path>
                                <path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="mt-6 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
                            Vizyonumuz
                        </h3>
                        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
                            Türkiye'nin en güvenilir dijital çözüm ortağı olmak.
                            İnovatif yaklaşımlarımız ve kaliteli hizmetlerimizle
                            sektörde öncü konuma gelmek ve global pazarda yer
                            almak.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- VALUES SECTION -->
    <section class="bg-gray-50 py-20 lg:py-28">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
                <h2
                    class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
                    Değerlerimiz
                </h2>
                <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600">
                    İş yapış şeklimizi belirleyen temel prensiplerimiz
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-2xl lg:max-w-none">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 lg:grid-cols-3">
                    <div class="text-center">
                        <div
                            class="mx-auto flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-indigo-100">
                            <svg
                                class="h-8 w-8 text-indigo-600"
                                fill="none"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                stroke-width="1.5"
                                stroke="currentColor">
                                <path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    d="M9.813 15.904L9 18.75l-.813-2.846a4.5 4.5 0 00-3.09-3.09L2.25 12l2.846-.813a4.5 4.5 0 003.09-3.09L9 5.25l.813 2.846a4.5 4.5 0 003.09 3.09L15.75 12l-2.846.813a4.5 4.5 0 00-3.09 3.09zM18.259 8.715L18 9.75l-.259-1.035a3.375 3.375 0 00-2.455-2.456L14.25 6l1.036-.259a3.375 3.375 0 002.455-2.456L18 2.25l.259 1.035a3.375 3.375 0 002.456 2.456L21.75 6l-1.035.259a3.375 3.375 0 00-2.456 2.456zM16.894 20.567L16.5 21.75l-.394-1.183a2.25 2.25 0 00-1.423-1.423L13.5 18.75l1.183-.394a2.25 2.25 0 001.423-1.423L16.5 15.75l.394 1.183a2.25 2.25 0 001.423 1.423L19.5 18.75l-1.183.394a2.25 2.25 0 00-1.423 1.423z"
                                ></path>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="mt-6 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
                            İnovasyon
                        </h3>
                        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
                            Sürekli öğrenmeyi ve gelişimi benimser, en güncel
                            teknolojileri projelerimizde kullanırız.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="text-center">
                        <div
                            class="mx-auto flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-purple-100">
                            <svg
                                class="h-8 w-8 text-purple-600"
                                fill="none"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                stroke-width="1.5"
                                stroke="currentColor">
                                <path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12c0 1.268-.63 2.39-1.593 3.068a3.745 3.745 0 01-1.043 3.296 3.745 3.745 0 01-3.296 1.043A3.745 3.745 0 0112 21c-1.268 0-2.39-.63-3.068-1.593a3.746 3.746 0 01-3.296-1.043 3.745 3.745 0 01-1.043-3.296A3.745 3.745 0 013 12c0-1.268.63-2.39 1.593-3.068a3.745 3.745 0 011.043-3.296 3.746 3.746 0 013.296-1.043A3.746 3.746 0 0112 3c1.268 0 2.39.63 3.068 1.593a3.746 3.746 0 013.296 1.043 3.746 3.746 0 011.043 3.296A3.745 3.745 0 0121 12z"
                                ></path>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="mt-6 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
                            Kalite
                        </h3>
                        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
                            Her projede mükemmelliği hedefler, kaliteli iş
                            çıkarma konusunda hiçbir ödün vermeyiz.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="text-center">
                        <div
                            class="mx-auto flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-pink-100">
                            <svg
                                class="h-8 w-8 text-pink-600"
                                fill="none"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                stroke-width="1.5"
                                stroke="currentColor">
                                <path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    d="M15.75 6a3.75 3.75 0 11-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 017.5 0zM4.501 20.118a7.5 7.5 0 0114.998 0A17.933 17.933 0 0112 21.75c-2.676 0-5.216-.584-7.499-1.632z"
                                ></path>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="mt-6 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
                            Müşteri Odaklılık
                        </h3>
                        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
                            Müşterilerimizin ihtiyaçlarını dinler, onların
                            başarısını kendi başarımız olarak görürüz.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- TEAM SECTION -->
    <section class="py-20 lg:py-28">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
                <h2
                    class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
                    Ekibimiz
                </h2>
                <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600">
                    Deneyimli ve tutkulu profesyonellerden oluşan ekibimiz
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-2xl lg:max-w-none">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2">
                    <div
                        class="flex flex-col items-center text-center lg:flex-row lg:text-left">
                        <div class="mb-6 lg:mr-8 lg:mb-0">
                            <div
                                class="flex h-32 w-32 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-600 to-purple-600">
                                <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-white"
                                    >VD</span
                                >
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
                                Geliştirici Ekibimiz
                            </h3>
                            <p class="font-medium text-indigo-600">
                                Frontend & Backend Uzmanları
                            </p>
                            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
                                Modern teknolojilerde uzman, yaratıcı çözümler
                                üreten deneyimli geliştiricilerimiz
                                projelerinizi hayata geçiriyor.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div
                        class="flex flex-col items-center text-center lg:flex-row lg:text-left">
                        <div class="mb-6 lg:mr-8 lg:mb-0">
                            <div
                                class="flex h-32 w-32 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-600 to-pink-600">
                                <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-white"
                                    >VD</span
                                >
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
                                Tasarım Ekibimiz
                            </h3>
                            <p class="font-medium text-purple-600">
                                UI/UX Tasarım Uzmanları
                            </p>
                            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
                                Kullanıcı deneyimini ön planda tutan, estetik ve
                                fonksiyonel tasarımlar oluşturan yaratıcı
                                tasarımcılarımız.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA SECTION -->
    <section
        class="bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-600 via-purple-600 to-pink-600 py-20 lg:py-28">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
                <h2
                    class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl">
                    Birlikte Çalışmaya Hazır mısın?
                </h2>
                <p class="mt-6 text-xl leading-8 text-blue-100">
                    Projenizi gerçeğe dönüştürmek için bizimle iletişime geçin.
                    Size özel çözümler geliştirmeye hazırız.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-10">
                    <a
                        href="/iletisim"
                        class="inline-flex items-center rounded-lg bg-white px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-600 shadow-lg transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-gray-50 hover:shadow-xl">
                        İletişime Geç
                        <svg
                            class="ml-2 h-5 w-5"
                            fill="none"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            stroke-width="1.5"
                            stroke="currentColor">
                            <path
                                stroke-linecap="round"
                                stroke-linejoin="round"
                                d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</PageLayout>
